---
// Editor mockup illustrating a pending AI suggestion (content rewrite + visibility reveal).
// Static, non-interactive. Lifted from design tooling and adapted to the site's theme tokens.
---

<figure class="suggestion-demo not-prose">
  <div class="page-frame">
    <div class="page-body">
      <div class="page-head">
        <h2 class="page-headline">The Warehouse on Drake Street</h2>
        <div class="head-meta">
          <div class="crumbs">
            <span>Duskvol</span>
            <span class="sep">/</span>
            <span>Crow&apos;s Foot</span>
            <span class="sep">/</span>
            <span class="crumb-current">Drake Street</span>
          </div>
          <div class="edited">Edited 2 minutes ago</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="blk blk-p is-hover">
        <div class="handles">
          <button class="h-btn" type="button" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button class="h-btn" type="button" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <svg width="10" height="14" viewBox="0 0 10 14" fill="currentColor"><circle cx="2" cy="3" r="1.2"/><circle cx="2" cy="7" r="1.2"/><circle cx="2" cy="11" r="1.2"/><circle cx="8" cy="3" r="1.2"/><circle cx="8" cy="7" r="1.2"/><circle cx="8" cy="11" r="1.2"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
        Three storeys of soot-blackened brick. The sign over the gate still reads <strong class="smallcaps">Saggek &amp; Sons, Cooperage</strong>, but nobody has rolled a barrel out of it in a generation.
      </div>

      <div class="blk blk-p">
        <div class="handles">
          <button class="h-btn" type="button" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button class="h-btn" type="button" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <svg width="10" height="14" viewBox="0 0 10 14" fill="currentColor"><circle cx="2" cy="3" r="1.2"/><circle cx="2" cy="7" r="1.2"/><circle cx="2" cy="11" r="1.2"/><circle cx="8" cy="3" r="1.2"/><circle cx="8" cy="7" r="1.2"/><circle cx="8" cy="11" r="1.2"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
        The Bluecoats walk past it twice a night. They never look up.
      </div>

      <div class="blk blk-p is-locked">
        <span class="lock-badge">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
          Locked
        </span>
        <span class="lock-text">Inside, the ground floor is empty.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="connector"></div>

      <div class="proposal">
        <div class="origin-mark" title="From your familiar">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="prop-eyebrow">
          <span class="label">Proposal &middot; Content</span>
          <span class="verb">Rewrite</span>
          <span class="spacer"></span>
          <span class="pulse"></span>
          <span class="pulse-text">Awaiting your decision</span>
        </div>
        <p class="prop-body">Inside, the ground floor is mostly empty: a few collapsed crates against the back wall, a tarpaulin draped over something the size of a small boat, and the smell of old whale oil that won&apos;t quite leave.</p>

        <div class="prop-provenance">
          <span class="raven-mark" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Suggested by your familiar after the Session 3 review &middot; 2 minutes ago</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prop-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-accept" type="button" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Accept
            <span class="kbd">&crarr;</span>
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-reject" type="button" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6 6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            Reject
            <span class="kbd">Esc</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="blk blk-p is-gm-only is-locked gm-spacing">
        <span class="lock-badge">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
          Locked
        </span>
        <span class="lock-text">But the trapdoor at the back, half-hidden under a bolt of canvas, is oiled. Recently.</span>
        <span class="vis-eye" title="GM only">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="connector"></div>

      <div class="proposal is-visibility">
        <div class="origin-mark" title="From your familiar">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="prop-eyebrow">
          <span class="label">Proposal &middot; Visibility</span>
          <span class="verb">Reveal</span>
          <span class="spacer"></span>
          <span class="pulse"></span>
          <span class="pulse-text">Awaiting your decision</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vis-change">
          <span class="vis-chip from">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
            GM only
          </span>
          <span class="vis-arrow">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span class="vis-chip to">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="3"/><path d="M3 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h4a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2"/><circle cx="17" cy="7" r="3"/><path d="M21 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/></svg>
            Players
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="vis-quote">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          <span>Found in <span class="cite">Session 3 &middot; 0:42:27</span></span>
        </p>

        <div class="prop-provenance">
          <span class="raven-mark" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Suggested by your familiar after the Session 3 review &middot; just now</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prop-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-accept" type="button" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Accept
            <span class="kbd">&crarr;</span>
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-reject" type="button" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6 6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            Reject
            <span class="kbd">Esc</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <figcaption>
    Editor mockup: a content rewrite and a visibility change, both pending the GM&apos;s decision.
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .suggestion-demo {
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .suggestion-demo figcaption {
    margin-top: 0.875rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ===== Page (the editor) ===== */
  .page-frame {
    background: var(--background);
    border: 1px solid rgb(28 25 23 / 0.06);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6) inset,
      0 30px 60px -30px rgba(90, 74, 106, 0.18),
      0 0 0 1px rgb(28 25 23 / 0.02);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  :global(.dark) .page-frame {
    border-color: rgb(231 229 228 / 0.08);
    box-shadow:
      0 30px 60px -30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5),
      0 0 0 1px rgb(231 229 228 / 0.04);
  }

  .page-frame::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgb(28 25 23 / 0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(28 25 23 / 0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 32px 32px;
    background-position: -1px -1px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    pointer-events: none;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, black 30%, transparent 90%);
  }
  :global(.dark) .page-frame::before {
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgb(231 229 228 / 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(231 229 228 / 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
  }

  .page-body {
    padding: 40px 64px 48px 64px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .page-head .head-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 14px;
  }

  .page-head .crumbs {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .page-head .crumbs .sep { opacity: 0.35; }
  .page-head .crumbs .crumb-current { color: var(--foreground); }

  .page-head .edited {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    opacity: 0.85;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .page-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  /* ===== Block (editor row) ===== */
  .blk {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6px 0;
    transition: background 150ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }
  .blk + .blk { margin-top: 8px; }
  .blk-p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }
  .smallcaps {
    font-variant: small-caps;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* drag/insert handles in left gutter */
  .handles {
    position: absolute;
    left: -56px;
    top: 8px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2px;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 150ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .blk.is-hover .handles { opacity: 1; }
  .h-btn {
    width: 20px;
    height: 22px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: rgb(28 25 23 / 0.4);
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: default;
  }
  :global(.dark) .h-btn { color: rgb(231 229 228 / 0.4); }

  /* ===== Suggestion treatment ===== */

  .blk.is-locked {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 18px;
    margin-left: -18px;
  }
  .blk.is-locked::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 6px;
    bottom: 6px;
    width: 2px;
    border-left: 2px dashed color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 35%);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .blk.is-locked .blk-p,
  .blk.is-locked .lock-text {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--foreground), transparent 35%);
    cursor: not-allowed;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .blk.is-locked .lock-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: rgb(184 149 48 / 0.1);
    padding: 2px 8px 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-right: 8px;
    vertical-align: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Connector — between locked block and proposal */
  .connector {
    position: relative;
    margin: 6px 0 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    margin-left: -18px;
    height: 16px;
  }
  .connector::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: -4px;
    width: 18px;
    height: 22px;
    border-left: 2px dashed color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 35%);
    border-bottom: 2px dashed color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 35%);
    border-bottom-left-radius: 12px;
  }

  /* The proposal panel */
  .proposal {
    position: relative;
    margin-left: -18px;
    margin-right: -18px;
    padding: 18px 22px 18px 22px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 92%) 0%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 96%) 100%
      ),
      var(--background);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px -4px rgb(184 149 48 / 0.15);
  }

  .proposal .origin-mark {
    position: absolute;
    left: -8px;
    top: -10px;
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-gold);
    color: #fff;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px -2px rgb(184 149 48 / 0.35), 0 0 0 4px var(--background);
  }
  .proposal .origin-mark svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; }

  .proposal .prop-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .proposal .prop-eyebrow > * { white-space: nowrap; }
  .proposal .prop-eyebrow .label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    padding-right: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .proposal .prop-eyebrow .verb {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    background: rgb(184 149 48 / 0.12);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .proposal .prop-eyebrow .spacer { flex: 1; }
  .proposal .prop-eyebrow .pulse {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgb(184 149 48 / 0.5);
    animation: suggestion-pulse 2.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes suggestion-pulse {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgb(184 149 48 / 0.5); }
    50%      { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgb(184 149 48 / 0); }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .proposal .prop-eyebrow .pulse { animation: none; }
  }
  .proposal .prop-eyebrow .pulse-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .prop-body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--foreground);
    margin: 4px 0 0;
  }

  .prop-provenance {
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding-top: 12px;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 80%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
  }
  .prop-provenance > span:not(.raven-mark) {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .prop-provenance .raven-mark {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgb(90 74 106 / 0.1);
    display: inline-grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .prop-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .btn {
    appearance: none;
    border: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    cursor: default;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    transition: all 150ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .btn-accept {
    background: var(--color-gold);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px -8px rgb(184 149 48 / 0.4);
  }
  .btn-reject {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-left: auto;
  }
  .btn .kbd {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 10px;
    background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.25);
    border: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 0.3);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-left: 2px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .btn-reject .kbd {
    background: rgb(28 25 23 / 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgb(28 25 23 / 0.1);
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
  }
  :global(.dark) .btn-reject .kbd {
    background: rgb(231 229 228 / 0.05);
    border-color: rgb(231 229 228 / 0.1);
  }

  /* ===== GM-only block (right gutter eye + halo) ===== */
  .gm-spacing { margin-top: 18px; }
  .blk.is-gm-only { position: relative; z-index: 0; }
  .blk.is-gm-only::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    right: -24px;
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      rgb(90 74 106 / 0.14) 0%,
      rgb(90 74 106 / 0.10) 40%,
      rgb(90 74 106 / 0.04) 75%,
      transparent 100%
    );
  }
  .blk .vis-eye {
    position: absolute;
    right: -24px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .blk.is-locked .vis-eye {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary), transparent 40%);
  }

  /* ===== Visibility proposal preview ===== */
  .proposal.is-visibility {
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary), transparent 75%) 0%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary), transparent 86%) 30%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 88%) 65%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gold), transparent 78%) 100%
      ),
      var(--background);
